<title>表格</title>
<h4 align="center">超级简单的表格</h4>
<b>例1：</b>无表头
<table border="1" align="center";>
	<tr>
    	<td>100</td>
        <td>200</td>
        <td>300</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
    	<td>400</td>
        <td>500</td>
        <td>600</td>
    </tr>
    
</table><br /><br /><br />
<b>例2：</b>表头
<table border="1" align="center">
	<tr><!-表头th->
    	<th>姓名</th>
        <th colspan="2">电话</th>
        <th>爱好</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
    	<td>tom</td>
        <td>0001</td>
        <td>0002</td>
        <td>football</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
    	<td>lily</td>
        <td>1001</td>
        <td>1002</td>
        <td>pingpang</td>
    </tr>
	
</table><br /><br />
<b>例3：</b>垂直的表头
<table border="2" align="center">
	<tr>
    	<th>姓名</th>
        <td>张三</td>
        <td>李四</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
    	<th rowspan="2">电话</th>
        <td>1111</td>
        <td>2222</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
    	<td>3333</td>
        <td>4444</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
    	<th>爱好</th>
        <td>跑步</td>
        <td>游泳</td>
    </tr>
</table>

</body>
